      <title>中国与日本、韩国峰会聚焦供应链</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/china-japan-and-south-korea-start-first-summit-talks-since-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国、日本和韩国在自 2019 年以来首次正式三方峰会上寻求重振安全和经济事务合作，李强总理希望说服邻国与北京合作保持供应链稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/china-japan-and-south-korea-start-first-summit-talks-since-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 01:07:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列在拉法袭击中袭击帐篷城，数十人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/dozens-killed-as-israel-strikes-tent-city-in-assault-on-rafah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯管理的卫生部表示，周日晚间，以色列对南部城市拉法的一个流离失所者营地发动空袭，造成至少 35 名巴勒斯坦人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/dozens-killed-as-israel-strikes-tent-city-in-assault-on-rafah</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 22:50:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国警告中国工业威胁整个全球经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/china-s-industry-threatens-entire-global-economy-france-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，整个世界经济都面临着中国廉价出口产品过剩的风险，同时七国集团也提出了一系列联合批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/china-s-industry-threatens-entire-global-economy-france-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平的中国电动汽车梦想成真。十年过去，围墙正在筑起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/xi-s-china-ev-dream-came-true-10-years-on-walls-are-going-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十年前的今天，习近平主席在参观中国最大的汽车制造商之一上汽集团的几款豪华轿车时发表了一次关键讲话，这将使中国走上主导电动汽车行业的道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/xi-s-china-ev-dream-came-true-10-years-on-walls-are-going-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国《金融时报》称，比尔·格罗斯预计特朗普获胜将扰乱债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/bill-gross-expects-trump-win-to-disrupt-bond-markets-ft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国《金融时报》报道，比尔·格罗斯表示，唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统大选中获胜将比乔·拜登获胜对债券市场更具破坏性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/bill-gross-expects-trump-win-to-disrupt-bond-markets-ft-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 20:36:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立陶宛总统纳乌塞达以压倒性优势赢得第二任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/russia-hawk-nauseda-poised-to-win-second-term-as-president-in-lithuania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛总统吉塔纳斯·瑙塞达周日当选，开始第二个五年任期，这个波罗的海国家的选民绝大多数支持外交政策的连续性以及对俄罗斯侵略威胁的强硬路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/russia-hawk-nauseda-poised-to-win-second-term-as-president-in-lithuania</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 19:25:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜通报计划将间谍卫星送入轨道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/north-korea-notifies-japan-of-impending-satellite-launch-kyodo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜已通知日本，计划于 6 月 4 日前发射一枚火箭部署一颗卫星，试图在首次成功发射数月后将其第二次间谍探测器送入轨道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/north-korea-notifies-japan-of-impending-satellite-launch-kyodo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 18:37:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列军队不顾法院裁决继续进入拉法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/war-in-gaza-israeli-military-proceeds-into-rafah-despite-world-court-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管国际法院以保护平民为名下令停止此类活动，但以色列军方仍在加沙南部城市拉法继续对哈马斯采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/war-in-gaza-israeli-military-proceeds-into-rafah-despite-world-court-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 10:13:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中方敦促韩方保持供应链稳定畅通</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/china-japan-leaders-head-to-seoul-for-first-summit-since-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国要求韩国保持稳定的供应链，这是两国自2019年以来首次与日本举行三方峰会，李强总理还会见了三星电子公司负责人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/china-japan-leaders-head-to-seoul-for-first-summit-since-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 01:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克的国民服务计划面临资金和执行问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/sunak-pledges-mandatory-national-service-in-uk-election-gambit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在竞选中承诺恢复英国年轻人的国民服务，但这一承诺立即受到了外界质疑，即这项耗资 25 亿英镑（32 亿美元）的计划将如何获得资金并实施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/sunak-pledges-mandatory-national-service-in-uk-election-gambit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
